### Verify Leader
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sync/c74760ff-be48-4ebb-a940-c91a3b7b1e44/verify-leader
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leaderPasscode": "1111"
}

### Update Sync
PUT http://localhost:5002/api/sync/ac2deeea-1c6e-4722-9bb5-2fdbf74d45cb
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Sync Title",
  "description": "Updated description for the sync.",
  "timeZone": "America/New_York",
  "timeSelector": [
    {
      "date": "2026-05-05",
      "startTime": "2024-07-01T09:00:00Z",
      "endTime": "2024-07-01T17:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "leaderPasscode": "1111"
}

